keyFacts: The document is an email dated August 13, 2020, from an FBI Special Agent identified as 'IMMIMIE'.
The email forwards a Suspicious Activity Report (SAR) related to Squad C-20, which investigates Crimes Against Children and Human Trafficking.
The attached SAR is dated August 14, 2020, suggesting ongoing investigative activity in that timeframe.
The communication originates from the FBI's New York office, indicating the geographic focus of the investigation.
